+ ./download -h
download - Sample minimal application without commands

Usage:
  download SOURCE [TARGET] [options]
  download --help | -h
  download --version | -v

Options:
  --help, -h
    Show this help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

  --force, -f
    Overwrite existing files

Arguments:
  SOURCE
    URL to download from

  TARGET
    Target filename
    Default: same as source

Examples:
  download example.com
  download example.com ./output -f

